Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.30,0:00:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 第三个可能最怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说够了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 我跟山本做过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的净是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亏你净想出那种过分的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是第三个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是玩笑也好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.20,0:01:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论什么事 我都接受
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:54.85,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:02:00.75,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:06.72,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:12.62,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:19.75,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:24.75,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.71,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:39.25,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:44.23,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:51.42,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:56.25,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.27,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:54.85,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:02:00.75,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:06.72,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:12.62,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.92,0:02:19.75,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:24.75,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:31.01,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:39.25,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:44.23,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:51.42,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.93,0:02:56.25,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:58.27,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经三天了 没和矢野说话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟山本做过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白隐瞒不是矢野狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是对我温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那是奈奈的妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.10,0:03:39.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野寂寞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说那是对奈奈的讽刺？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个 背叛的都是矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 矢野一个也没投进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 真少见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 男生考试呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小学到现在一直体育5分的记录…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 容易受心情影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没当运动员真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我会当恋爱小说家的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就你那平均分B的作文 没戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情节是我自己 有好多吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算吧 意外的有些不中用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说男的不中用是夸奖的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比中用感觉好一百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过驳回 你不过是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么打手机她都不接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不看我一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.20,0:05:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多打几次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打了五十次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那打一百次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀哎呀真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得人家特意来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我不想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 七美正洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说洗澡 说睡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在见了只会说冲动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我理解你的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可现在还是缓和一下好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等情绪稳定了事情才会顺利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等明天七美…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保证有明天吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀真是的 好漂亮的花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请转告她 明天学校见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.40,0:06:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去要当心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么美丽的花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可七美你真是的 鬼一样的姑娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想用这花让我上钩么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会啊 别开玩笑了 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多么勇敢啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那勇敢的少年 和前女友的妹妹做过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是漂亮的花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他妈妈精心栽培吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看 这么多玫瑰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 傻瓜 像傻瓜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香 肯定是慌慌张张从院子里摘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用报纸简约地包来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的抱着这么大一束花 乘公交车来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想重写过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么事都会做的 只要你不哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.20,0:07:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么晚去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去车站牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可矢野 可能也痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想臭骂他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可只能说出这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.60,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我好天真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我也许还没原谅他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可一看见他就想 这是无可奈何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心 可还是想在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是喜欢就认输了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小水之前就说 你是胜不过死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可过去无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只考虑现在的幸福就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野恨着奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不想说死人的坏话 也没见过她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 奈奈好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要让矢野幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟傻瓜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啊 好了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我可以给你些忠告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有煎熬的恋爱 还是算了的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.40,0:10:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幸福呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周日上哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 去动物园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我说去动物园你还当我傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去看猴子吧 猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没心情看猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有心情看啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 看海
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.80,0:10:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人还真喜欢海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可这儿的海跟照片里的不一样 也好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去吧 去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 能重来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人 会选择不同的人生么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海带
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 打住啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择相遇的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.60,0:11:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只选择幸福的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波光粼粼的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 挺好挺好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉那边可以呐 当成是床
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有幸福的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是那样 该有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集贝壳吧 我带瓶子来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.10,0:11:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形状不好的不行 要没缺口的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集这个干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做为回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 我能说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到内裤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有樱贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.70,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱贝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种漂亮的 必须去更南边些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.60,0:12:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野我好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 是海蟑螂 海蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.30,0:12:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 讨厌 讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会咬你的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里也有 讨厌讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去 我要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我太吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 才刚到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 讨厌虫子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不算讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我和谁弄混了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请忘掉奈奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说谎背叛你 让你孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你生气是当然的 恨是理所应当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想抱怨 却说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为奈奈已经死了不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在说吧 矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说的话 怨恨的也好什么也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么也没有啊 事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那种事 你肯定有想说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.00,0:14:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好唠叨啦 都说了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人火大 混蛋 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.50,0:14:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好听的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果奈奈在这儿 你会说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.10,0:15:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们是有里的同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能不能借我点钱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没付账就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这就是盲目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没有真心喜欢过别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这才叫做乳臭未干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也快谈一次真正的恋爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为他会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你还等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.80,0:15:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了积攒怨气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:16:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}姐姐 那个不是怀炉 是喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我该怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？自己的事情自己考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是白痴啊 想不出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你绝对要按我说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样会让我幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.80,0:16:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是谁都不哭泣 不生气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有打架没有乱扔东西的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们两人去寻找幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}如果现在遇到 你会说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说你想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说谎了 说的话和办的事都充满矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说好了不背叛你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不背叛我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}没有第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那么喜欢的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望你活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要让你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创造不输给过去的现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓 向星星大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.90,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星划过的话 我愿和七七永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野 我不能再继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法让矢野你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能信守约定 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.40,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野的愿望 早就注定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不怨恨 就像被悲伤压垮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是矢野的自我防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好我约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要离开我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}人为什么要约定无法遵守的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满意了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.40,0:22:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时也说活该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到高桥这么没毅力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又想被安慰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵 我不会再上你的当
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.40,0:22:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都有过梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有过幸福的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在后悔得要死
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.60,0:25:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时那处 我选择的言行总是错误连篇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.00,0:25:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可希望你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.50,0:25:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥 我对你…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨那些话 是最后通牒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.30,0:25:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过你会后悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.30,0:25:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.60,0:25:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经无路可退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:12.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}季節が少し動いた気がする
